Added the fitness website

This commit adds the complete fitness website including  a  Flask application (`app.py`, `main.py`, `routes.py`, `utils.py`),  templates (`templates` directory), static files (`static` directory), and Replit configuration files (`.replit`, `pyproject.toml`, `replit.nix`).  The website generates personalized diet and workout plans.

